Package org.tquadrat.foundation.stream.internal

@API(status=INTERNAL, since="0.1.0") package org.tquadrat.foundation.stream.internal
The internal classes for the stream extensions.

    Description
    org.tquadrat.foundation.stream
    The code in this package was originally written by Dominic Fox and provided in the package com.codepoetics.protonpack.
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    AggregatingSpliterator<I>
    An implementation of Spliterator that aggregates the elements of the stream based on a provided Predicate.
    DefaultMapStream<K,V>
    The default implementation for MapStream.
    InterleavingSpliterator<T>
    A selector function takes an array of values and returns the respective array index for the selected value.
    MergingSpliterator<T,O>
    An implementation of [@link Spliterator} that merges streams.
    SkipUntilSpliterator<T>
    An implementation of [@link Spliterator} that skips elements on the stream that do not match the provided condition.
    TakeWhileSpliterator<T>
    An implementation of Spliterator that takes elements from a stream while the given Predicate returns true.
    UnfoldSpliterator<T>
    An implementation of Spliterator that which takes a seed value and applies a generator to create the next value, feeding each new value back into the generator to create subsequent values.
    ZippingSpliterator<L,R,O>
    An implementation of Spliterator that zips two streams into one.
